<h2>Dossier Brasilien - Letras do Brasil (Zeitschriftenheft)</h2>
<h3></h3>
<hr>
<abbr class='unapi-id' title='2223'></abbr>
<div class='row-fluid'>
<div class='span8'>
<h3>Allgemeine Angaben</h3>
<h4>Herausgeber</h4>
<a href="/pers/176-Enrique_Rodrigues_Moura" class="tag multiline" popup="true">Enrique Rodrigues-Moura</a>
<span class='tag multiline'>Ursula Prutsch</span>
<p class='space-l'></p>
